because I was always say, even when checkout,

00:02:35.190 --> 00:02:38.250
"Here's my website," so they
can see that I'm legitimate.

00:02:38.250 --> 00:02:42.110
And people sometimes write me and
say, "Do you know such and such

00:02:42.110 --> 00:02:43.310 position:56%
